# Cloud Run overlay only needs the Dockerfile + entrypoint script.
# Everything else (openclaw source, docs, etc.) is in the upstream base image.
#
# .gitignore-style: `*` excludes everything; `!` re-includes. Re-including
# a file inside an excluded directory requires re-including the directory
# first, so we take a two-step approach for `scripts/`.

*

!Dockerfile.cloudrun

!scripts
scripts/*
!scripts/cloudrun-entrypoint.sh

# Never include credentials or local state, even if accidentally renamed.
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.openclaw
**/.gcloud
**/.config
